'''Docking Bay 3732''' was a spacecraft [[Hangar/Legends|docking facility]] that was part of [[Eastport/Legends|Eastport's]] [[Gate 3700]]. The [[Kuat/Legends|Kuati]] [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Viqi Shesh]] kept her personal [[Yacht/Legends|star yacht]], the ''[[Wicked Pleasure]]'' there.

